      <title>加拿大最古老的公司Hudson's Bay试图避免完全清算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/canada-s-oldest-company-hudson-s-bay-hbc-tries-to-avoid-full-liquidation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈德森湾公司（Hudson&#39;s Bay Co.）周一避免在多伦多法庭上完全关闭，要求允许本周开始清算其大部分商店。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/canada-s-oldest-company-hudson-s-bay-hbc-tries-to-avoid-full-liquidation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 20:59:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国顶级法院拒绝更多试图停止债务刹车投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/german-top-court-rejects-more-attempts-to-stop-debt-brake-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国最高法院驳回了额外的企图，以防止国家即将离任的议会对宪法进行更改，以消除国防借贷的限制，并建立了5000亿欧元（5460亿美元）的基础设施基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/german-top-court-rejects-more-attempts-to-stop-debt-brake-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 20:59:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
