      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 18:46:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保守派承诺杀死加拿大的工业碳税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/conservatives-promise-to-kill-canada-s-industrial-carbon-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大的保守派领导人承诺，如果当选，则保证该国的工业碳价格取消，但对企业的影响程度将取决于省份是否效仿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/conservatives-promise-to-kill-canada-s-industrial-carbon-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 15:55:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对新鲜的胡塞威胁加大对伊朗的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-ramps-up-pressure-on-iran-with-fresh-houthi-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对伊朗的压力施加了压力，要求他们遏制霍蒂斯（Houthis），如果也门的武装组织没有阻止其袭击，就提高了对伊斯兰共和国进行报复罢工的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-ramps-up-pressure-on-iran-with-fresh-houthi-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 15:43:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
